<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registation Page</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="heading">Exam Registration Form</h1>
    <p>Clearly fill the form below and ensure to indicate the courses registered for.</p>
    <hr>
      
   <div class="m-4 row justify-content-center">
    <form action="scusses" method="post">
    <div class="col-sm-6 ">
        <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control " id="name" placeholder="Enter Your Name">
      </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
  <label for="email" class="form-label">Email address</label>
  <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control " id="email" placeholder="name@example.com">
</div>
<div class="col-sm-6">
    <label for="number" class="form-label">Mobile Number</label>
    <input type="number" name="number" class="form-control " id="number" placeholder="Your Mobile NO.">
</div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 mt-3">
    <input type="submit">
  </div>
</form>
   </div>
</body>
</html>